    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for your next great project? This vehicle is ready for a transformation! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for anyone who loves to roll up their sleeves and bring a car back to life. It's an affordable entry point for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a rewarding challenge!",
