    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently has difficulty starting and exhibits a consistent knock, while the transmission shows signs of slipping. The exterior has several noticeable dents and rust spots, and the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This car is best suited as a project for a dedicated mechanic or as a donor vehicle for parts.",
      "price": 4500.0,
