      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard that warrants the highest classification of excellence. This specimen exhibits an immaculate aesthetic and mechanical profile, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original showroom debut. Every detail, from the pristine coachwork to the refined interior appointments, remains in flawless condition. This is a rare acquisition for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
